title: Hum Hain Kamaal Ke
subTitle: Two men with hearing and speech impairments run a grocery store. When a man is murdered in their store by an underworld gang who are after stolen diamonds, they try their hand at solving the case.

title: Tathagat Buddha
subTitle: Lord Buddha was born as Prince Siddhartha Gautama in Kapilavastu, Nepal, in the 6th century B.C. Renouncing worldly pleasures, he left his wife and son to seek salvation.

title: Khoj
subTitle: Ravi and Anita's vacation turns into a nightmare when Anita vanishes without a trace. Ravi's frantic search leads to more questions than answers when a woman appears, claiming to be his missing wife.

title: Adharm
subTitle: Mr Verma's decision to disown his son Jaggan sparks a vow of retribution. Years later, Jaggan devises a plan to destroy his family and retaliate against his father.

title: Thank God
subTitle: An egotistical real estate broker comes face-to-face with God after meeting with an accident. Soon, he is forced to play a game that will put him either in heaven or hell.

title: Main Khiladi Tu Anari
subTitle: A Bombay police officer seeks revenge when a drug dealer kills his brother. However, things get complicated when a film star begins to tag along, so that he can research a film role.

title: Khoonkhaar
subTitle: Gagan, a brave young man, is unable to be with Sweety, his true love, due to her parents' disapproval of him. However, he vows to protect her after unknowingly saving her from gangsters.

title: Hamara Dil Aapke Paas Hai
subTitle: When Preeti stands up against a murderer in court, she suffers a devastating consequence. Later, after being rejected by her loved ones, she finds shelter and support in an empathetic stranger.

title: Valimai
subTitle: Arjun, a police officer, sets out on a mission to hunt down a group of violent bikers after they are involved in a theft and murder. When a city's crime rate rises, it is up to Arjun, a police officer, to restore order.

title: Jung
subTitle: Desperate to save his son's life, Veer, an honest cop, is faced with an impossible choice when he discovers that the only person who can help him is a notorious criminal behind bars.

title: Jung

title: Swarnakamalam
subTitle: Meenakshi, a young classical dancer who was born in a family of artists, is bitter about the lack of opportunity in India. However, Chandrashekhar changes her outlook and helps her grow.

title: Insaniyat Ke Devta
subTitle: Two friends, Balbir and Anwar, join forces to defeat an influential tycoon who wishes to destroy an ashram and use the property to further his own selfish purposes.

title: Fillers
subTitle: A comprehensive compilation of promotional videos and trailers of Bollywood movies featuring popular actors and actresses.

title: Velaiilla Pattadhari
subTitle: Raghuvaran, an educated yet unemployed engineer, is unwilling to accept jobs that are unrelated to his area of expertise. Soon, his mother's tragic death brings him a job as well as grave challenges.

title: Rahul
subTitle: Caught in the emotional crossfire between his divorced parents, an innocent 5-year-old becomes collateral damage, and inevitably, this takes a toll on his health.

title: Ek Vivah Aisa Bhi
subTitle: A tragedy compels Chandni to put off her marriage and singing career. As she takes on new responsibilities, Prem holds their love in his heart for years, and waits for the day when she can come back to him.

title: Naseeb Apna Apna
subTitle: A naive village girl marries the son of a domineering man. However, upon her arrival at his house in the city, she finds out that he is already married.

title: Mard
subTitle: Azad, a wealthy prosperous king, is locked in a dungeon by General Dyer who wants to take over his kingdom. Years later, Azad's son comes to his father's rescue and puts an end to Dyer's tyranny.

title: Toofan
subTitle: Separated at birth, the paths of Shyam, a lousy magician unwittingly roped into a crime, and Toofan, a defender of the people, cross again years later as they reunite to avenge their father.

title: Gunda Gardi
subTitle: Karan Singh, a police officer, is called in to help arrest Kalicharan and Narshima, two brothers who have caused problems all over the city.

title: Jai Mahashakti
subTitle: The king of Travancore is ruthless and tortures his subjects. However, Vaikundasamy, an incarnation of Lord Vishnu, decides to put an end to this tyranny.

title: Afsana Dilwalon Ka
subTitle: A gifted singer, Banne Khan, falls in love with Saba. However, Titlibai, a woman who wants him to marry her daughter, invites him to stay at her house.

title: Love U Ganesha
subTitle: Chintu always complains to Lord Ganesha about the hard work that he has to do as a fifth-grader. Lord Ganesha decides to help him in his own unique way.

title: Hello Charlie
subTitle: Charlie, a good-for-nothing young man, becomes entangled in fast-paced, side-splitting monkey business between a runaway gorilla and a high-profile wanted fraudster disguised as one.

title: Sabse Bada Khiladi
subTitle: Inspector Vijay infiltrates a rich businessman's family to investigate the death of his twin brother and exact revenge on the murderer.

title: Shaadi Mein Zaroor Aana
subTitle: Satyendra and Aarti meet for an arranged marriage and end up falling in love with each other. Their lives, however, change completely when she runs away on their wedding day.

title: Andaaz
subTitle: After his sweetheart Kajal marries another man, Raj moves to Cape Town. He eventually agrees to marry Jiya but is shocked to find that she is Kajal's widowed sister-in-law.
